title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, when there is no data returned, the output parameter is not displayed in the 'Edit Data Set' dialog.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps: 
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database. 
2. Check the query result which is stored in the output parameter as an object. The output parameter should be displayed in the 'Edit Data Set' dialog.
